# Cloudflare Pages — redirect rules
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# API proxy: forwards /api/* to the Worker so the app can use relative paths.
# After deploying the Worker, replace the placeholder with your Worker URL
# (shown at the end of `wrangler deploy` output, or in the Cloudflare dashboard
# under Workers & Pages → infobuilder-worker → Settings → Domains).
#
/api/*  https://infobuilder-worker.infobuilder.pages.dev/api/:splat  200
